\xa0\xa0(a) The Employment Term of this Agreement shall terminate upon; 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(i) the expiration of the Initial Term or Renewal Term (whichever then applies) if one party gives the other party written notice of intent not to renew this Agreement at least one hundred and eighty (180)\xa0days before the expiration of the Initial Term or Renewal Term then in effect; or 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(ii) the occurrence of one of the following early termination events: 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(A) Executive’s death or permanent disability or incapacity (as determined by the governance committee of the Parent’s Board of Directors in their good faith judgment); 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(B) the mutual agreement of the Company and Executive; 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(C) Company’s termination of this Agreement for Cause or without Cause; or 
\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0(D) Executive’s termination of this Agreement for Good Reason or without Good Reason.'
